is your cat naughty what do they do that's naughty when one of my kittens sees that i'm heading toward the bathroom he runs ahead of me and jumps on the seat so i can't sit down he likes to see the flush weird i know but i don't think he knows that the flush doesn't come until after a certain point the other one steals my make up brushes and get cat spit all over them i have one cat that likes to sit on our coffee table and if you have a drink like a glass of water sitting on the table be will start lightly batting at it so you won't notice he then pushes it really hard off of the table he really enjoys tipping over drinks its weird though he never goes after cans of soda i have another cat that loves to drink out of the bath tub its not really naughty but more annoying because he will stand on the edge of the tub and just meow and meow until he gets what he wants my fiance's parents came to visit us we didn't even tell them about the cat and the tub but by the time i came home from work while they were there dillinger our kitty had already trained them to turn on the tub for him Friends Cat RuneScape quests Poker jargon Garfield Toilet Customs and etiquette of Japan Jackass: The Movie Codename: Kids Next Door Badly Drawn Kitties The Shining (film) Silent Night, Deadly Night Shaggy dog story "Weird Al" Yankovic Avenue Q Looney Tunes and Merrie Melodies filmography Ranma __ characters Table tennis Trailer Park Boys The Grim Adventures of Billy and Mandy Okashina Okashi Matt Hardy Ty Cobb Pitaten Little Britain Homer Simpson Kitchen Spidey Super Stories __douard Manet Bong Futurama (TV series - season 2) Draw poker Austin Powers The Smoking Room Humphrey Bogart Girly Japanese toilet Minor characters in Seinfeld Recurring South Park characters Sin City Swimming pool Professional wrestling aerial techniques Fecal incontinence Tea Ocean's Twelve President (game) Ron Weasley The Brady Bunch Eric Cartman Babe Ruth Ron and Fez Prince Edmund (Blackadder) Kim Possible Snooker